    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition. It runs and drives, but has some mechanical issues that should be addressed. The exterior shows visible wear including minor dents and scratches. The interior has noticeable use with some staining and wear on the upholstery. It is functional for daily use but will likely require some maintenance or repairs in the near term.",
